      "value": "<p>At 8th level, you can force a defeated creature to accept a binding pact as a condition of its surrender, as if you are using lesser geas, except the creature must have a number of Hit Dice equal to or less than your cleric level. At 16th level, this ability functions as per geas/quest. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your Wisdom modifier.</p>\n<p>This power replaces the Staff of Order power of the Law Domain.</p>"
